- Bagus sekali.
- Sangat cantik.

118
00:08:15,410 --> 00:08:16,690
Tarian Qingqing sangat bagus.

119
00:08:17,730 --> 00:08:19,780
Menurutmu, tanda lahir rubah
di tubuhnya itu,

120
00:08:20,170 --> 00:08:21,690
